><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1362-2461\">Martin Lopez Howe</a></p>  <p>Mousa lies here. Christos.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Orsi 1893 308 no. 124 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001715</a></li><li> Wessel 1989 311 no. 1788 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000394</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Letters are rubricated</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
